headline: GE Aerospace Board of Directors Authorizes Regular Quarterly Dividend
summary: EVENDALE, Ohio, December 13, 2024--The Board of Directors of GE Aerospace (NYSE: GE) today declared a $0.28 per share dividend on the outstanding common stock of the Company. The dividend is payable January 27, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on December 27, 2024. The ex-dividend date is December 27, 2024.
